metadata.name: Azuki Kyoto Garden
metadata.description:
This NFT will serve as an event ticket for participation in the Azuki Kyoto Garden event, which will be held on June 29, 2023 in Kyoto, Japan.

First NFT made by Azuki Japan community members.

Want to make the Azuki community more active.  
With this in mind, Azuki Japan members have come together to create the Ticket NFT for the event on June 29th.

▼Event  
Date 29th June 2023  
Place Kyoto in Japan  
The venue will be announced from the Azuki Japan twitter account(@AzukiJapan_IKZ).

▼Music by Sire (Twitter account @SDP808OD)  
Music name "kyoto"

▼Art by  
Yuka(Twitter account @kamogawayuka)  
YQ(Twitter account @YQNFT)  
NarumiS ナルミ(Twitter account @narimatsu413)  
WAKA(Twitter account @WAKA_NFT)  
武にぃ(Twitter account @TAKE_NFT,@TAKE_N1i)  
Mika Sawae(Twitter account @SawaeMika)  
つむぎ(Twitter account @kinoco012)  
ak(Twitter account @ak_ism49)  
闇鍋(Twitter account @yami_nabe_10)  
Eri Harigai(Twitter account @eri_harigai)  
Izuru Shinonome(Twitter account @grifonbk)

▼Calligraphy by Tashimaya(Twitter account @ArtSumica)
